Package gw.api.databuilder

Class EmploymentDataBuilder

java.lang.Object
gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<EmploymentData,EmploymentDataBuilder>
gw.api.databuilder.CCDataBuilder<EmploymentData,EmploymentDataBuilder>
gw.api.databuilder.EmploymentDataBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
DelegateDataBuilder<EmploymentData>, ValueGenerator<EmploymentData>
public class EmploymentDataBuilder extends CCDataBuilder<EmploymentData,EmploymentDataBuilder>
Builder for EmploymentData, which is a sub object of either Claim or Exposure and describes a person's employment information. Because EmploymentData can be associated with either a Claim or Exposure, and is used in several different places in the UI, there is no UI ready builder for EmploymentData. The builder is typically used together with a claim or exposure builder, for example: claimBuilder.withEmploymentData(new EmploymentDataBuilder()...)
